```c
/** The silent recipient for each output or null for a regular address. */
const secp256k1_silentpayments_recipient *tx_output_recipient_ptrs[N_TX_OUTPUTS];
```

(the description here is more important than the name, just `recipient_ptrs` is probably fine)

